summary: Store conformance tests (PostgreSQL + DynamoDB)
description: |
    Runs the 31-test conformance suite against PostgreSQL and DynamoDB+S3
    (via DynamoDB Local + rustfs containers). SQLite and inmem conformance
    run as part of the unit tests.
test: bash tests/conformance/run.sh
duration: 10m
require:
    - golang
    - docker
    - docker-compose
    - curl
framework: shell
